{"type":null,"faqId":38469,"title":"相机设置","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>在拍照界面，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125283\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125284\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，可对相机进行设置：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“分辨率”：设置相机的分辨率。视频分辨率可在录像界面点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125285\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125286\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 分辨率”，进行设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“地理位置”：开启后，拍摄的照片或视频将包含地理位置信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“优先存储位置”：设置将拍摄的照片或视频默认存储到 SD 卡或手机内存中。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“魅我”：开启或关闭“美肤”模式中自动识别特定面容、进行定制美化的功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“ISO”：设置照片的 ISO。通过增大 ISO，可以降低由黑暗或对象移动造成的图像模糊。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“白平衡”：设置照片的白平衡。根据光照条件调整照片的色彩平衡。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>“图像调整”：调整照片的曝光补偿值、饱和度、对比度和亮度。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":1,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3749","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441442756000,"seriesProductName":"GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10","visitedTimes":150,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"相机设置","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}